event.title: Richard Stallman gives a talk about "Free software, GNU and GCC" in Prague, Czeck Republic

body.p: On July 9, Richard Stallman gives a talk about "Free software, GNU and GCC" at GNU Tools Cauldron 2012, Prague. The event will take place at room S9, Department of Maths and Physics, Charles University, Malostranske Namesti 25, Prague from 10.00 to 10.45.
